-- Banco do Brasil sees fee income recovering in coming quarters
-- By Guillermo Parra-Bernal
-- Wed May 07, 2014 10:08AM EDT
-- None



SAO PAULO, May 7 (Reuters) - Fee income at state-run Banco do Brasil SA <BBAS3.SA> should gain traction in the coming quarters, Chief Financial Officer Ivan Monteiro said on Wednesday.

Banco do Brasil SA, the nation's largest bank by assets, missed first-quarter profit estimates after fee income declined sharply And fell short of estimates.